title: Prepare for the Eclipse!

speakers.name: Steven Swenson
speakers.bio: Steven is a developer with Rackspace.

excerpt:

description:
Attention budding astronomers!!
In April there will be a total solar eclipse in the Eastern United States!!!  This is a big deal, so let's get together and talk about what an eclipse is, when it will happen, and how to safely view it. AND we will also be building solar eclipse viewers from cardboard boxes. (All supplies provided.)
